      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_The Times UK_0801@magazinesclubnew_page_083_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "his tour is a wonderful blend of some of the finest sights in northern Italy. Firstly, Lake Garda, where waves lap gently on the shingle shoreline, with the snow-capped Dolomite mountains in the background; then Venice, a unique city full of cultural delights such as the Doge's Palace, St Mark's Basilica and the Grand Canal,; astly, Verona, one of the most romantic cities you will ever find.",
